params.name: pixel_values
params.type: torch.FloatTensor of shape (batch_size, num_channels, height, width)
params.description: Pixel values. Pixel values can be obtained using AutoImageProcessor. SeeMaskFormerImageProcessor.call() for details.

params.name: pixel_mask
params.description: Mask to avoid performing attention on padding pixel values. Mask values selected in [0, 1]:1 for pixels that are real (i.e. not masked),0 for pixels that are padding (i.e. masked).What are attention masks?

params.name: output_hidden_states
params.description: Whether or not to return the hidden states of all layers. See hidden_states under returned tensors formore detail.

params.name: output_attentions
params.description: Whether or not to return the attentions tensors of Detrs decoder attention layers.

params.name: return_dict
params.description: Whether or not to return a ~MaskFormerModelOutput instead of a plain tuple.
